        jTextArea5.setText("This college information System consists of four region:\n          1. Menu bar region present at the top of interface.\n          2. Form region for filling  and adding the college details at the left side of interface.\n          3. Table region showing the details of college present in the College Information System \n               at the right side of interface.\n          4. Search college region at the buttom right of interface. \n\nThe menu bar consists of file and help option. Inside file there are open file and exit file menu items.\nThe open file will open the \"CollegeIS.txt\" file containing the details of college saved in college infor-\nmation system. And the exit option will close teh College Information Sytem.\nInside help option there is user guide menu items which contains the breif details of the College inf-\normation System.\n\nIn form region there are different text fields, combo boxes, radio buttons, and a add college button.\nThe add college button will save the inserted details to the table.\n\nIn table all the saved details of College are displayed.\n\nIn search college region we can search college according to college fee or college category. ");
        jTextArea5.setBorder(javax.swing.BorderFactory.createTitledBorder(""));
        jScrollPane5.setViewportView(jTextArea5);

