        jTextArea1.setText("Some notes for user before adding college deatils to College Information System\n\nNote 1: Each College has unique College ID.\nNote 2: The deatils of college with two same college ID is not saved in college Information system\nNote 3: All the field in the form should be inserted or selected to save college details.\nNote 4: While inserting college details in the form, there should be only one space between 2 word.\n           i.e. Informatics_College not Informatic__College (here \"_\" denotes space)\nNote 5: The fee should be in number format .i.e., 10000, 20000, etc.");
